          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-arz0hdymv-2e9d6ea2-f946-437c-b448-da2fffbdc68a",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "傾聴:"
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-arz0hdymv-d0eb7eca-5d81-4ae6-b666-dbe0d9400338",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 患者さんの話を丁寧に聞き、共感する姿勢を示します。話の内容だけでなく、表情や態度からも患者さんの気持ちを理解しようと努めることが大切です。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-t1o5uni6b",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-hlw96l7ye-56a20735-f5a6-469b-b5e4-d49b27430d4f",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "*   "
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-hlw96l7ye-1b06614a-30a0-4227-a15c-fe5e32f753ed",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "受容:"
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-hlw96l7ye-1d28c7a0-0b8a-4091-9973-ed225de4efa5",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 患者さんの考えや感情を否定せず、受け入れる姿勢を示します。たとえ理解できない言動があったとしても、頭ごなしに否定するのではなく、まずは受け止めることが重要です。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-rciusmlhk",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-p47iintqj-ea8f3959-c640-4042-8fdb-b0320a6dc8d0",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "*   "
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-p47iintqj-770119b6-5297-4f42-836b-0407256f35c2",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "励まし:"
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-p47iintqj-f09f4cfc-26ce-4cf7-b102-36acad2f5f68",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 患者さんの良いところを見つけ、積極的に褒めることで、自信を持てるように励まします。「〇〇さんがいてくれると、病棟が明るくなります」など、具体的な言葉で伝えることが効果的です。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-foopfxj0l",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-cpy53o3qd",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "精神科の患者さんは、言葉でうまく表現できない気持ちを抱えていることもあります。相手の立場に立って、非言語的なコミュニケーションも意識しながら、寄り添う姿勢が大切です。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-ojilzed0j",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-ii5ati7pm",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "安全な環境の維持"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h3"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-3dg8kojy0",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-8pt4mwisy",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "精神科病棟では、患者さんの安全を守るために、常に危険がないか注意を払う必要があります。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-udaqax026",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-lomf59gok-83348386-d2ac-4bf2-af7b-bc1682e538e1",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "*   "
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-lomf59gok-0a57942e-831a-4e8f-ac27-ce58658f3692",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "危険物の管理:"
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-lomf59gok-9fbe81bf-6d27-429b-84de-b06c987551e5",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " ハサミやカミソリなど、患者さんが自傷行為に使う可能性があるものは、厳重に管理します。使用後はできるだけ回収し、紛失がないか確認することが重要です。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-dx1wfu9xt",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-iqjhw7wtp-61693278-22ac-46cd-ba2b-02b070f5c410",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "*   "
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-iqjhw7wtp-3078e37c-be16-4c94-82c0-a8e34c2563a7",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "環境整備:"
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-iqjhw7wtp-9ae76858-d6a0-4d4d-ae6c-fd25d63588bb",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 病室や共有スペースに危険なものがないか、定期的に点検します。床に物が落ちていないか、配線がむき出しになっていないかなど、細かい点にも注意を払う必要があります。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-1i8gnujom",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-ljglqbumu-9d701d14-43a1-4f70-ac9e-63b49782bac5",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "*   "
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-ljglqbumu-fd677ece-d01b-44b2-a0e0-b089084a4e86",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "患者さんの見守り:"
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-ljglqbumu-b75fac4d-5548-4e80-8eb1-6eea47996853",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 患者さんの行動を観察し、異変があれば速やかに看護師に報告します。特に、自殺企図や自傷行為の兆候が見られる場合は、注意深く見守る必要があります。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-0j8mmw7lf",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-g4c8vq0iw",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "精神科病棟での具体的な業務内容"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h2"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-8la8js5en",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-t47aorwn0",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "精神科病棟での看護助手の業務は多岐にわたりますが、ここではより具体的な内容を掘り下げて解説します。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-h8dp4uayq",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-qa9gdwkq0-81c9f192-8672-4976-8b9d-df4fb33000cc",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "*   "
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-qa9gdwkq0-ec8ca1e4-bd17-4438-bea3-ceda36da306c",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "レクリエーションの企画・実施:"
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-qa9gdwkq0-6c25df22-7ed7-432d-8524-f90ce3a5790d",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 患者さんの社会性や意欲の向上を促すため、レクリエーションの企画・実施をサポートします。例えば、簡単なゲームや歌、絵画、手芸など、患者さんが楽しめるような企画を考えます。患者さんの年齢や体力、興味関心などを考慮し、無理なく参加できるような内容にすることが大切です。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-r0vc8mk80",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-b5ocdsvdq-50e5c4ec-74b9-43a0-aa6b-3ab2e4bc1387",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "*   "
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-b5ocdsvdq-3fcf49c8-3743-4f7d-86cd-48015fd2c734",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "服薬状況の確認:"
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-b5ocdsvdq-30633d9f-3a38-49e5-9631-cd8cea74b696",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 患者さんが正しく服薬しているかを確認します。薬の種類や量、服用時間などを確認し、飲み忘れがないか、指示通りに服用しているかなどをチェックします。もし飲み忘れがあった場合は、看護師に報告し、指示を仰ぎます。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-5ttvn6t65",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-rue75iwz8-9f614f2c-ebc6-45e5-8a0e-5994e26f243f",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "*   "
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-rue75iwz8-5a9d5c27-3d4c-4588-b6ad-418cd195ba14",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "病棟内の清掃:"
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-rue75iwz8-5d1f7932-dd65-4e01-9ae1-c64961e7e54d",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 病棟内を清潔に保つことは、感染症予防の観点からも重要です。患者さんの使用するリネン類の交換、トイレ清掃、ゴミ捨てなどを行います。患者さんが快適に過ごせるように、常に清潔な環境を保つことが大切です。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-6l0c70a74",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-2jno69z6c",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "精神科看護助手に求められる資質"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h2"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-pj6430s01",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-8oopds90l",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "精神科看護助手には、以下のような資質が求められます。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-76ak3mvtr",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-46jz32u0i-5ccb4754-57d7-4546-b148-c3573f8c59fa",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "*   "
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-46jz32u0i-fb72d6a9-0f38-4759-9c01-2f2525b735b2",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "柔軟性:"
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-46jz32u0i-a7d633e8-3588-45b4-b1a2-d66ded071a67",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 患者さんの状態は日々変化するため、状況に応じて臨機応変に対応できる柔軟性が求められます。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-l55gca6u6",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-qa39kdhev-4e562e41-b2e3-4f63-b68a-14806108f148",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "*   "
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-qa39kdhev-368723fa-4e77-4a21-9e08-4831ce02fe0d",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "客観性:"
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-qa39kdhev-d2e93759-01ca-4b59-8299-3b44cb27fbe4",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 患者さんの感情に巻き込まれず、冷静に状況を判断できる客観性も重要です。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-cix6m7qoz",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-kh1386rlo-fbe27dfd-ed93-4c9e-8063-460164b67fb1",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "*   "
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-kh1386rlo-5773f637-44d7-4d0c-b0bd-6c59ed0ad3b9",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "倫理観:"
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-kh1386rlo-843d045a-75f2-46da-b5ce-12f0ddd9f14e",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 患者さんのプライバシーを尊重し、守秘義務を遵守する倫理観が求められます。患者さんの個人情報や病状などを、許可なく他人に話すことは基本的に避けなければなりません。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818215674-x9xjh8suu",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818215674-guu48liak",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "これらの資質を磨くことで、患者さんにとってより良いサポートを提供できるようになります。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "internal-link-4ee9f16f-2445-4375-b2f8-9d6118d8728c",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "internal-link-span-intro-a01c163c-0c7a-40cd-912b-a9f8b25b8755",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "詳しくは"
          },
          {
            "_key": "internal-link-span-title-f3ce8a5a-06f8-4ad5-95c2-72c89aa69c4e",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "link-810ac32e-0aa7-4ade-a696-3d6aaeb3d317"
            ],
            "text": "「精神科病棟で働く看護助手の一日とは」"
          },
          {
            "_key": "internal-link-span-outro-8d560839-a4c6-4148-87aa-7ca6cabd515b",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "でも現場のポイントを詳しく解説しています。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "link-810ac32e-0aa7-4ade-a696-3d6aaeb3d317",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "/posts/nursing-assistant-day-psychiatric-ward"
          }
        ],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "inline-link-b4b07d64-9915-44b9-b391-106a9d73abd9",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "inline-pr-37af64cd-c768-4442-8b13-23d0612d01f8",
